<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>non-rper001</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> ~ <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>/em I don't roleplay</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Fajon</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> ~ <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Get out of the my way Lightbringer trash...or I will invoke the wrath of my god upon you.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br>
<br>
Now here is what is taking place.<br>
All Fajon wanted the person to do was move, he didn't ask them to RP with him, just to move.  <br>
Was Fajon polite? Nope, Fajon is not polite.<br>
Was the person roleplaying Fajon trying to somehow offend the player of non-rper001?  Nope, just maintaing his character.<br>
<br>
Would it really have been hard to just move?  Don't have to say anything...nothing...just move.  I go on my merry way and so do you.  That is compromise, me stopping to send you a tell and apologizing for offending your delicate sensibilities..that is not compromise.<br>
<br>
Now that is a very simplistic example sure, but it works to show how things go vs how they should go between those RPing and those not.  <br>
<br>
If for some other reason you just <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>have</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> to play on the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>only</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> RP server out of the what 40? other servers, would it be so much to ask that you not be <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>ANTI</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->-RP?<br>
<br>
~~~<br>
<br>
/sigh, I don't know why I bother posting this stuff.  The people who don't get it most likely never will.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
