If negative RP interaction with someone that I am waiting for or that my activities depend on (critical raid members, friends, etc) causes  a) me to lose an opportunity b) others to lose an opportunity, or c) everyone to have a bad time because RP pissed someone off, then yes, it <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>does</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> affect me.<br>
