<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>You see people's personality as a shade of their roleplay, instead of people being wholly and entirely separate from their roleplay.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
